Ext.data.JsonP['Downloading_and_Installing_Studio']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Downloading and Installing Studio</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div id=\"banner\" class=\"confbox admonition admonition-note aui-message warning shadowed information-macro\">\n\t\t\t<p>You can now find Appcelerator documentation at <a href=\"https://docs.axway.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.axway.com/</a>. This site will be taken down in the near future.</p></div>\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-30083017\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Downloading and Installing Studio</h1>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083017_DownloadingandInstallingStudio-Contents\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Contents</span></h2>\n    <p>    </p>\n<ul class=\"toc-indentation \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Downloading_and_Installing_Studio-section-src-30083017_DownloadingandInstallingStudio-Overview\">Overview</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Downloading_and_Installing_Studio-section-src-30083017_DownloadingandInstallingStudio-InstallingAppceleratorStudio\">Installing Appcelerator Studio</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Downloading_and_Installing_Studio-section-src-30083017_DownloadingandInstallingStudio-InstallingTitaniumStudio\">Installing Titanium Studio</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Downloading_and_Installing_Studio-section-src-30083017_DownloadingandInstallingStudio-InstallingAptanaStudio\">Installing Aptana Studio</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Downloading_and_Installing_Studio-section-src-30083017_DownloadingandInstallingStudio-InstallationLocations\">Installation Locations</a>    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083017_DownloadingandInstallingStudio-Overview\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Overview</span></h2>\n    <p>This page describes how to download and install the IDE if you do not already have Eclipse installed.    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Eclipse users: download and extract the appropriate installer for Studio at <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Plugging_Studio_into_an_existing_Eclipse_configuration\">Plugging Studio into an existing Eclipse configuration</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Standalone Studio users: Complete the instructions on this page    </p>\n</li></ul>    <p><strong class=\" \">Prerequisite:</strong> Ensure your machine meets the <a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Setting_up_Studio-section-src-37540095_SettingupStudio-SystemRequirements\">Studio System Requirements</a>.    </p>\n    <div class=\"confbox admonition admonition-note aui-message warning shadowed information-macro\">\n            <p>On Windows Vista or Windows 7 you may need to set the <strong class=\" \">Run this program as an administrator</strong> property to true.    </p>\n    </div>\n        </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083017_DownloadingandInstallingStudio-InstallingAppceleratorStudio\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Installing Appcelerator Studio</span></h2>\n    <p>To download and install Appcelerator Studio:    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Log in to <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://platform.appcelerator.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://platform.appcelerator.com/</a>.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Expand the Appcelerator menu     <img src=\"images/download/thumbnails/30083017/appc_menu.png\" alt=\"images/download/thumbnails/30083017/appc_menu.png\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-thumbnail\" width=\"40\">\n and clicked on <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://platform.appcelerator.com/#/product/studio\" target=\"_blank\">Studio</a>.    </img></p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Download the installer or ZIP file for your operating system.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Launch the downloaded installer.    </p>\n</li></ol>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083017_DownloadingandInstallingStudio-InstallingTitaniumStudio\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Installing Titanium Studio</span></h2>\n    <p>To download and install Titanium Studio:    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Go to the <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"http://preview.appcelerator.com\" target=\"_blank\">downloads</a> page to download the installer or ZIP file for your operating system.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Launch the downloaded installer.    </p>\n</li></ol>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083017_DownloadingandInstallingStudio-InstallingAptanaStudio\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Installing Aptana Studio</span></h2>\n    <p>To download and install Aptana Studio:    </p>\n<ol class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Go to the <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"http://www.aptana.com/products/studio3/download\" target=\"_blank\">downloads</a> page for Aptana Studio and download the installer or ZIP file for your operating system.    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Launch the downloaded installer.    </p>\n</li></ol>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-30083017_DownloadingandInstallingStudio-InstallationLocations\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Installation Locations</span></h2>\n    <p>If you need to find the location of your installation on disk, here are the default installation locations:    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Windows: C:\\Users\\username\\AppData\\Local\\* Studio    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>OS X: /Applications/Aptana Studio 3, /Applications/Titanium Studio or /Applications/Appcelerator Studio    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=30083017\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Downloading and Installing Studio"});